title: Week 13 NFL Preview & Chris Rose Joins The Show
itunes:title: Week 13 NFL Preview & Chris Rose Joins The Show
description:
DJ and Bucky give their game-by-game Week 13 NFL preview (1:23), NFL Network & MBL Network host Chris Rose joins the show to discuss his hometown Cleveland Browns & the dilemma of a potential MLB-NFL decision for Oklahoma QB Kyler Murray (17:25), and they give their Championship week college football picks (42:15)
